              Medical Practice • RDV en ligne • PACS
            </p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm group-hover:gap-3 transition-all" style="color: var(--color-copper); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">
              View project
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" class="transition-transform">
                <path d="M6 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
